text: Marina Kuzhmar (born 3 January 1977 in Minsk, Belarus) is a Belarusian rower. She competed in the women's eight at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belarus Category:Rowers at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:1977 births
